values: ...really hates me, but it's working, finally. I need to change my layout and icon and everything so it looks cool. I also think I may just use this for ranting, as I really don't want my personal life broadcast for all to see. XP Oh well, this is a short entry.
The title says it all. I hate today.

w00t!! It's a lot of fun here, ne. I got a new messenger bag and a chain wallet for my birthday, and I get to play with the new puppy like 24/7. It's so cool. ^^ And I actually get to use the internet! Tis' very, very cool here. I wish I could move in. I'd have such an easier/better time if I did. But, alas, I care too much about my brothers to do that.... >< Ah well, I think I'm "in like" (love, but I don't want to say love until I'm sure...) But I'm not telling who. That ruins my whole illusion that he may actually go out w/ me.... ^^; I think I'm gonna ask him to Homecoming either next month or sept. Fun, ne? He completely makes me melt. I'm like putty.... I never felt this way about Paul, so I believe that I really need to rethink myself... Oh, yeah, I'm more of an otaku than ever! KO all the way!

Today was a pretty cool day! I got to sit at home by myself while my mum and Jim went to Parts-a-reme with my bros!!! It was awesome-ness, lol, so quiet. ^^! Penn State in 7 days, woot!

Oh yeah, comment on my art on deviantart.com, please! My username is 0okumagoroubeamo0

A lot of things have happened since I was last onnnnn.... someone please fill me innnnnnnnnnn............... Geh. I need to know stuff. I wish someone would you know, call me, or something to that effect. i'm really blind to everything. if it wernt for Joelle and Julia, I would know just about nothing. Wait, I do know nothing. ><;;;;;;;;
OTAKU (or should I say otaco?) KENNYWOOD DAY WAS THE BEST! I was soooo excited to be included in the awesomeness of that day! I thank Jo-tan for inviting me.

Ah, here's me back to elaborate on the previous entry! W00t!! I'm qwert's new fangirl, lol, and very dedicated. ^^; So it seems anyway. Heh, Kennywood was the bomb. Thanks to Tim, for the ride, and thanks to Jo-tan for organizing. Oh, and thanks to qwert for protecting me from the evil creepiness of //whispers a name that Jo-tan and I are afeared of\\ You know who I mean, lol. I had a total blast. I can't wait to see you all again. //big dewy Haku eyes\\

Wow, yesterday was the bestest day ever. I had Qwert, Jo-tan, and Tommy over, and we had so much fun. We played DDR and watched Anime, and played strip poker- strike that from the record. Nobody really stripped, though, Jo-tan kept losing LOL!!!!! 
Go KO, Our new comics rule the world!! Jo-tan and I think of some pretty odd things at 4 am... ^^;;;;;;;;;;;; Don't ask....... Oh, and we went swimmimng in the not so freezing pool. ^^ Ah, what a great day.
I leave for my Dad's house at 10am tomorrow. eight days away from this place. How fun

Monday was the bestest!! I got my hair cut all short and stuff!! It's so much more convenient now... ^^; I also can't wait till Penn State and my BDay par-t, cause I'll see everyone again!! ^-^
Hnnn.. oh yeah!! My mom pulled some strings at school and got me back into honors, so I'm really glad, cause I didn't wanna be back in CP classes... Bleh

^_^ Keeping the journal aliiiive. I can't wait till' the 27th!! I'm going to Penn State for a week!! WOOT!! ^x^

Oh, and I found out that 6/9 is Paul's birthday, ironic, eh? ^^; I'm gonna buy him a hat, lol

I don't know what to do about anything any more. I'm pretty sure Paul is going to go out with that whorish senior, cause she's a whore, and I don't- I ... I don't even feel like being alive anymore. I find it odd that I'm bothering with my journal, but writing comforts me... 
I had to take seven tylenol to fall alseep last night.
Maybe I'll just take the whole bottle tonight. Nobody would notice.

Kennywood was uber-fun. I got to hang out with everyone!! ^_^ The best- oh that had to be the raging rapids. I really miss Wang, lol, and I'm sure Skott misses being uber-wet. ^^ We played DDR the night b4, so my feet hurt really bad, but it was so worth it. I got to hang out with Dru, and Jess, and Manda, and Ranna, Skott, Kayla, and Josh- who looked like a lesbian, lol. ^^ My aunt Kathy thought he was a lesbian, lol She told me so. 
I really want to go back now, cause being at home sucks... ><
I got to see my cousins Marshall, Mayellen, and Al yesterday. They're hics from Tennessee, lol. But they are really cool. I tried to kick Al's friend in the head, but he moved. ^^ I realy wanted to hit him, cause he beeped at our car on his little-ass motor scooter and I had to restrain my mom from running him over. 
//sighs\\ 
I dunno. I'm in a really confused and mixed up mood at the moment. Everything is backwards. Especially with my feelings... I don't know- Paul is so uber-cool... and I really want to go out with him, but he hates me. I don't know what I did. Maybe I'm just a loser? 
><
Kennywood's tomorrow! I believe I'm going to Manda's tonight. w00t!! I'm gonna bring my PS2 so we can play DDR and we'll have sooo much fun. ^^ I'm in such a spunky mood.

;-; I don't feel like being here today. Paul said no... and gave me some lame ass pre-made excuse about working. I believe he's working, but... I think someone may have told him I was going to ask beforehand, so he had the excuse ready. --* Meh. Life sucks. I don't think I'm gonna go to Kennywood.
Wahh. My leg hurts like a monkey's uncle. --;;;; //sighs discontentedly\\ Eh. No sleep. NEED sleep. Oh, yeah, meh. Just keeping the journal alive.
I'm feeling hyper and powerful today. I think I'm gonna do it! Courage is something I'm going to need a lot of. No wonder I drank so much Pepsi this morning. ^^!
I tried, once again, to ask Paul out. But everyone in lunch made me so nervous... --; I couldn't do it. I want to ask him to Kennywood, but... I don't know. Maybe I'll try in study hall.

I tried again- to ask Paul out in homeroom, and yet again I failed. I just can't do it. ><;; //dies\\ I really can't. I don't have the nerve. Life sucks, major. Plus, poor Dru is stuck in that hell hole!! Jesseh is all mopey. ;_; Poor Jesseh. I shall cheer her up.

//bounces\\ Battle of the Bands was a lot of fun! ^^; I think it was... me, Dru, Jess, Ageh, Josh, Ranna, Larry, and a bunch of ppl I didn't know (including the other Jamie that was pretty cool, although I didn't get to talk to him... at all ^^*). //bounces to the Rancid pouring from her comp speakers\\ I'm writing this from home, ja... I can't write at school. It takes too much time. ^^* //sighs\\ Ja, but I stole *Paulie's* hat. lol, I love saying his name like that. It sounds all New York-ish, lol-ness It was amusing, cause he compared himself to a mop cause of his hair, and when I asked where the stick was he was like "Look at me! I *am* the stick!!" He's so cool when he wants to be, although I think I might still kind of like him... //looks at Jesseh, who is probably laughing\\ Ja, but I think Dru and I are on okay terms now. I dunno, he was really kind of cool at the Battle. ^^; Plus, he and Jess are genuinely *really* cute together. They actually make a really cool couple. So I figure, if they're happy, then why not let them be happy, you know? I've decided to drop the whole 'natalie-dru' issue. I figure, if I forget about it, then it won't cause anymore conflict. //shrugs\\ I don't even want to bother with it now. I mean, Natalie is my friend, and I defended her to the best of my abilities, but it sort of became a useless additional reason just to hate Dru. ><;; and I figure, if I don't want people to hate me, then why do I have the right to hate anybody? So that's it, I love everyone!! Yay!! //hugs everybody\\ >>; <<; ^^;
I don't feel like being here today. I want to go home and sleep. I think I'm sick. Damn brothers...... //dies\\

****journal from 2am, March 18, 2004****
****Ehmm... I- I'm kind of shook up... I- I don't know what to make of the dream I just had... First off, have you seen Little Nicky? It has to do with that... //sighs\\ Well, it started off like usual, you know, the FFX2 Oasis, the splashing, etc, and ended up with John kissing me once again, but this time... I- I let go to breathe for a second in the middle of the kiss and he- he was- he was Dru! It was so freaky!!! Then he said "What, no tongue?" and wiggled his tongue at me. (He did it like... like Adrian does to Nicky's girlfriend in Little Nicky. You'd have to see the movie to understand.) The worst part was that he was dressed as Seymour, whom I've become accustomed to associating with cute and cool-ness. I freaked and screamed in the dream and guess I screamed in my sleep. I think I woke myself up with my own shrieking.... >< It was so- scary! There's no other way to put it, seriously, absolutely no other word could describe that dream. I- I had to go and brush my teeth when I woke up!! Yich!! (No offense, Dru, it's just... well... I don't know what it *was*, it was bad, though. Bad even for your kind of perverted-ness.)**** 

****journal from around 9:00pm March 18, 2004****
****Yeah, I keep rereading that dream I had last night and... It's so- freaky! To think that happened the night before I tell Dru that I basically *hate* him. He called me a whiny bitch! I may be a bitch, but I'm not whiny unless I have to be. ><; Monk and Liz seem to agree with me. I don't know, I just don't think he should be saying things about Natalie even if he's never met her. He based his opinion of her on an opinion of a video game because of what she wore! He's always saying that people hate him and label him. Well, what do you call that? No it's not *labeling*, Dru would never *label* someone because of what they wore!!! //gags on the sarcasm\\ Gah, I hate people that contradict themselves. I'm not saying that I don't do it as well, but he does it far too often and I'm absolutely *sick* of it! ><; 
Anyway, on to happier topics! I almost beat someone up at lunch today. This chick keeps coming over to our lunch table and pissing me off! She's been doing it for about two weeks, and she's awful. Seriously, she called me ugly for the last time today. I know I'm nothing to look at but she had no room to talk. Ask anyone! Larry had to hold me back because I almost wailed on her ass. -_-; I really dislike her, and she drives me nuts, and she knows it, so its worse!! Grrr... ^^*
Yah, I wanna start a new story soon. Maybe I'll finish it! Wow! But that's a strech. I never finish anything. >< (Although I try my hardest....) Ah! And thanks to Rizu-sempai and Monk-sama for defending me. I feel uber-loved! Well now, I must be off to the shower-y goodness because it is nine thirty. //wanders away humming "Suteki Da Ne"\\****

I'm in a fair mood, although all of that crap happened Sat, Tekko was still soooo much fun, and I met an awesomr guy, and I rellay hope it can blossom into something more than friendship, but even if it does stay a friendship, thats okay, cause I really enjoy being his friend as well. Squirrel Ninjas unite!! Anyway, on the whole Jess and Dru matter, its okay, I really don't mind... It's not a big thing. You know, if they like eachother, then they have my best wishes as long as Dru is good to her, cause if he isn't, he'll have to deal with me on his ass. ><! Heh, I'm sure some people won't be as nice about it, but hey, what am I gonna do, you know? I love Jess and I don't want to lose her as a friend any more than I want to lose anyone else. I hope Liz isn't angry that I'm okay with this, even though she's not the type to be angry about something like this. ^^;;; Eh, I'm so excited about life in general. Tekko was so cool, and I made like a million new friends! Dac ("David"), John (Seymour), Ange(Lulu), and Natalie(Rikku), the Yohji chick, KT, Adam, Kenshin, and my date, Squall girl, little Vash, Alucard, and a whole bunch of others(the Yaoi man, and The Prince of Darkness with the evil Cloud) etc...). ^___^ Yes, Tekko, was fun-ness. I cannot wait till next year. ^___^ it's going to be very, very fun, cause I'm driving. ^^*

Yayyyyyy!!! The con is tomorrow, the con is tomorrow!! //dances around merrily in circles wearing Jo-chan's Kamui shirt\\ I cannot wait, I am soooo excited, so, so excited!! Hehehehehehehe!!!!! Anyway, I'm on a quiz rampage right now, so.... More quizzes cause I have nothing else to talk about and I'm bored.....

That is a great and sad movie, and Adam Sandler is hotter than ever, even his egg shaped head, lol

Ohhh yeah, Tekkosho-con in five days-es!! I am so incredibly excited. I'm gonna have so much fun and I really want to get me a boyfriend, cause I've never had one... and I really wan one-ness. Umm... I think thats all for today. ^^*

I'm so happy about my red-belt-ness. It's so exciting. I can't wait to start my new forms and self defense and board breaks. It's gonna be so fun. And I found out last night that Nate is bi, don't ask. I was watching his do his form last night and... wow... he's realllly good! I was so impressed, cause he's on demo team... and he does all that important stuff in TKD! Plus he's sooo hot, so hot, want to touch the hinie!! lol, I'm so happy right now. ^^* 

Oh, yeah, my mom said that I'm allowed to go to Tekkoshocon! I'm so excited cause I didn't get to go last year. I'm gonna cosplay and its gonna be so much fun-ness. I can't wait till then. Plus, this weekend is my biiig TKD tournament, at LaRoche college! i'm gonna go and kick some ass! Last tournament, as a brown belt, I brought home two thirds and a fourth (I was against four black belts and a red belt), but now as a red belt, I hope I can do better! ^^! I'm aiming for at least some second places. I really hope I do well.

I am an Amethyst Dragon!

Hey, I took the http://dragonhame.com online Inner Dragon quiz and found out I am a Amethyst Dragon on the inside. 

In the war between good and evil, a Amethyst Dragon tends to walk the fine line of Neutrality....
When it comes to the powers of Chaos vs. those of Law and Order, your inner dragon walks a fine line between Law and Chaos....
As far as magical tendancies, Magical spells come as natural to the Amethyst Dragon as breathe from it's body....
During combat situations, whether by spells or by claw, your inner dragon will do whatever it takes to get the job done....
The Amethyst Dragon makes its home in the deep caverns of the earth, often in mountainous regions. They spend much time in hibernation as one of their favorite things to do is to sleep.'
Formed from translucent amethyst, it is an awe inspiring sight to see one in it's true form. Light passes through the dragon's body creating a deep purple glow. It's scales will magnify the light rays into bright lavender beams to highlight this effect.'
Amethyst dragons spend most of their time homebound but do occasionally feel the need to take a sojourn to a far destination. These dragons love books and will often pick their destination from one of the many stories and histories they may have read. Amethyst dragons are very solitary in nature, but do keep a distant watch on the world around them. They tend to be highly intelligent, and often amuse themselves in human form by building gadgets and toys. Amethyst dragons are very learned creatures.
'
This Dragons favorite elements are: Amethyst, Deep Places, and Magic
